  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Sales Manager</strong></u></p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will lead the development and execution of sales and marketing strategies to expand the company’s customer base and achieve sales targets. Drive business growth by building and maintaining long-term relationships with targeted clients and business partners, leveraging your leadership and management expertise to deliver results.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and implement targeted sales and marketing strategies to increase market share and revenue</li><li>Lead and motivate sales teams to consistently achieve and exceed company sales targets</li><li>Build, grow, and sustain long-term relationships with clients and business partners to foster customer loyalty and repeat business</li><li>Manage the entire sales cycle, providing professional service from prospecting to closing deals</li><li>Identify and pursue new business opportunities to expand the company’s customer base</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams to align sales initiatives with overall business objectives</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in B2B and B2C sales, preferably within interior fittings, construction materials, retail, or related industries</li><li>Strong communication skills applied to negotiate and present solutions effectively to diverse stakeholders</li><li>Demonstrated determination and persistence in achieving sales goals</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Working Hours: 10am to 7pm</li><li>Benefits: Market competitive salary (Basic salary and commission), Career Development opportunities</li><li>How to Apply: Interested applicants, kindly click on “APPLY NOW”</li><li>Note: Only shortlisted candidates will be notified</li></ul>",
